This module introduces Product total price for every stock move, wich
can be selected as a measure in Move Analysis.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

To use this module follow this steps:

1. Go to Inventory -> Reporting -> Move Analysis
2. Now in Measures you will have a new field **Total Price**
3. Once this measure is selected the total price of the products based
   on the quantities and Sales price will be displayed in the pivot
   view.

